		 Do NOT rely on custom permissions to ensure that only the app can call reach components. That may not be
		 always true, like on KitKat and below because of the FakeID vulnerability and a custom permissions security
		 vulnerability. So that means, if the app is to support those (currently, yes), then it can NOT rely on custom
		 permissions for anything important (or anything at all). -->

